      <title>路透调查显示，一半日本企业认为特朗普再次当选总统存在风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/half-japanese-firms-see-another-trump-presidency-risk-reuters-poll-shows-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周四的一项调查显示，大约一半的日本企业认为唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统对企业构成潜在风险，保护主义加剧的前景是担忧的主要原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/half-japanese-firms-see-another-trump-presidency-risk-reuters-poll-shows-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 23:17:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西淡水河谷表示其索塞戈铜矿运营许可证已被吊销</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-vale-says-its-sossego-mine-operating-license-has-been-suspended-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西矿商淡水河谷周三表示，已收到帕拉州环境部长的一封信，通知其索塞戈矿的运营许可证已被暂停。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazils-vale-says-its-sossego-mine-operating-license-has-been-suspended-2024-02-21/</guid>
