      <title>皇家加勒比因邮轮需求强劲而上调年度利润预测</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/royal-caribbean-boosts-annual-profit-forecast-strong-cruise-demand-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[皇家加勒比集团周三上调了年度利润预期，因为该公司受益于关键“浪潮季节”期间强劲的游轮需求和强劲的船上支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/royal-caribbean-boosts-annual-profit-forecast-strong-cruise-demand-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 23:11:45 GMT</pubDate>
