      <title>Etsy 预测第一季度因可自由支配需求低迷而悲观</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/etsy-forecasts-downbeat-first-quarter-sluggish-discretionary-demand-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Etsy Inc 周三警告称，由于对其在线市场上销售的手工制品和个性化礼品的需求疲软，第一季度商品销售总额（GMS）下降。]]></description>
