      <title>标准普尔 500 指数、道指小幅收涨；英伟达盘后上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-dip-ahead-high-stakes-nvidia-results-fed-minutes-2024-02-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔 500 指数和道琼斯工业指数周三小幅上涨，而纳斯达克指数连续第三个交易日收低，因投资者等待英伟达公布的财报，该财报可能决定股市的近期动能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-dip-ahead-high-stakes-nvidia-results-fed-minutes-2024-02-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:55:45 GMT</pubDate>
